title: Neffland Interviews
description:
http://www.neffheadwear.com/snow 

Mark Copeland, Neff team manager, and Jeremy Cooper, Park City Mountain Resort terrain park manager, discuss the making of Neffland. Neffland is a new terrain park set in the Park City Mountain Resort in Utah, U.S.A. Listen as some of the features of Neffland are discussed, and also listen to Neff snowrider Sage Kotsenburg's insight on the new terrain park.
